title: American Cancer Society Updates Breast Cancer Screening Guideline (American Cancer Society)
text: ( Source : American Cancer Society ) October 20 , 2015-An updated breast cancer screening guideline from the American Cancer Society recommends that women at average risk start regular annual screening using mammography at age 45 and transition
